{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja template for CA-S04 runtime write-lane retirement wave-1 readiness (authority posture, lane statuses, blocker taxonomy, and deterministic next action). #}
{# Version: 2026.05.05.1 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-05-05 #}

{% set invalid = ['', 'none', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'None', none] %}

{% set shadow_entity = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' if states['sensor.shadow_active_target'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set shadow_exists = states[shadow_entity] is not none %}

{% set write_controls = state_attr(shadow_entity, 'write_controls') if shadow_exists else {} %}
{% if write_controls is not mapping %}{% set write_controls = {} %}{% endif %}

{% set scheduler_validation = state_attr(shadow_entity, 'scheduler_validation') if shadow_exists else {} %}
{% if scheduler_validation is not mapping %}{% set scheduler_validation = {} %}{% endif %}

{% set authority_mode = (write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls.authority_mode is defined else 'unknown') %}
{% set scheduler_apply = write_controls.scheduler_last_apply if write_controls.scheduler_last_apply is defined and write_controls.scheduler_last_apply is mapping else {} %}
{% set auto_select_attempt = write_controls.auto_select_last_attempt if write_controls.auto_select_last_attempt is defined and write_controls.auto_select_last_attempt is mapping else {} %}

{% set scheduler_apply_status = (scheduler_apply.status if scheduler_apply.status is defined else 'never_attempted') %}
{% set auto_select_status = (auto_select_attempt.status if auto_select_attempt.status is defined else 'never_attempted') %}
{% set scheduler_ready = (scheduler_validation.ready_for_scheduler_use if scheduler_validation.ready_for_scheduler_use is defined else false) %}
{% set scheduler_verdict = (scheduler_validation.verdict if scheduler_validation.verdict is defined else 'missing') %}

{% set lc6_l01_status = 'ready' %}
{% set lc6_l01_reasons = [] %}
{% if authority_mode != 'component' %}
  {% set lc6_l01_status = 'blocked' %}
  {% set lc6_l01_reasons = lc6_l01_reasons + ['authority_not_component'] %}
{% endif %}
{% if scheduler_ready == false or scheduler_verdict != 'PASS' %}
  {% set lc6_l01_status = 'hold' if lc6_l01_status != 'blocked' else lc6_l01_status %}
  {% set lc6_l01_reasons = lc6_l01_reasons + ['scheduler_not_ready_for_retirement'] %}
{% endif %}

{% set lc6_l03_status = 'hold' %}
{% set lc6_l03_reasons = ['metadata_override_helper_storage_still_compat'] %}

{% set component_backend = states('sensor.component_backend_profile') %}
{% set component_api = states('sensor.component_ma_api_url') %}
{% set lc6_l05_status = 'ready' if component_backend not in invalid and component_api not in invalid else 'hold' %}
{% set lc6_l05_reasons = [] if lc6_l05_status == 'ready' else ['component_backend_or_api_unresolved'] %}

{% set blockers = namespace(items=[]) %}
{% if lc6_l01_status != 'ready' %}
  {% set blockers.items = blockers.items + ['lc6_l01_not_ready'] %}
{% endif %}
{% if lc6_l03_status != 'ready' %}
  {% set blockers.items = blockers.items + ['lc6_l03_not_ready'] %}
{% endif %}
{% if lc6_l05_status != 'ready' %}
  {% set blockers.items = blockers.items + ['lc6_l05_not_ready'] %}
{% endif %}

{% if scheduler_apply_status in ['blocked_authority','blocked_debounce','blocked_reentrancy','blocked_option_mismatch','blocked_no_candidate'] %}
  {% set blockers.items = blockers.items + ['helper_writer_guard_blocked'] %}
{% endif %}

{% set retirement_ready = lc6_l01_status == 'ready' and lc6_l03_status == 'ready' and lc6_l05_status == 'ready' and (blockers.items | length == 0) %}
{% set verdict = 'PASS' if retirement_ready else ('WARN' if shadow_exists else 'FAIL') %}

### CA-S04 Runtime Write-Lane Retirement Validation
- Result: **{{ verdict }}**
- Shadow entity: **{{ shadow_entity }}** (exists={{ shadow_exists }})
- Authority mode: **{{ authority_mode }}**
- Scheduler readiness/verdict: **{{ scheduler_ready }} / {{ scheduler_verdict }}**
- Scheduler apply status: **{{ scheduler_apply_status }}**
- Auto-select status: **{{ auto_select_status }}**

### Wave-1 lane readiness
- `LC6-L01` active-target writer lane: **{{ lc6_l01_status }}** (reasons={{ lc6_l01_reasons }})
- `LC6-L03` metadata override helper-storage lane: **{{ lc6_l03_status }}** (reasons={{ lc6_l03_reasons }})
- `LC6-L05` server-profile/API helper-stack lane: **{{ lc6_l05_status }}** (reasons={{ lc6_l05_reasons }})

### Retirement blocker taxonomy
- retirement_ready: **{{ retirement_ready }}**
- blockers: **{{ blockers.items }}**

### Deterministic next action
{% if not shadow_exists %}
- Shadow entity missing. Load `custom_components/spectra_ls` and retry.
{% elif authority_mode != 'component' %}
- Set authority to component mode, then rerun this template.
{% elif lc6_l05_status != 'ready' %}
- Stabilize component backend/API surfaces (`sensor.component_backend_profile`, `sensor.component_ma_api_url`) before wave-1 retirement claims.
{% elif lc6_l01_status != 'ready' %}
- Resolve scheduler readiness and guard blockers before retiring active-target writer lane.
{% elif lc6_l03_status != 'ready' %}
- Keep metadata override helper storage in bounded compatibility mode; record explicit defer rationale.
{% else %}
- Wave-1 lanes are ready for retirement progression in this snapshot.
{% endif %}
